278
00:16:05,655 --> 00:16:07,756
I have a routine.

279
00:16:09,125 --> 00:16:11,259
I brush my hair 100 times

280
00:16:11,327 --> 00:16:13,895
just like I did when I was a little girl,

281
00:16:13,963 --> 00:16:16,164
