with her fingertips.

302
00:17:17,486 --> 00:17:19,355
And she looks at herself?

303
00:17:20,861 --> 00:17:22,466
Yes, she does.

304
00:17:26,074 --> 00:17:28,775
She's amazing.

305
00:17:28,842 --> 00:17:30,843
I sit at my vanity

306
