325
00:18:30,642 --> 00:18:32,309
The opportunity passed.

326
00:18:32,376 --> 00:18:34,544
Well, then we shall endeavor to recreate it.

327
00:18:34,611 --> 00:18:36,512
Perhaps lunch today?

328
