with what God gave you.

352
00:19:57,410 --> 00:19:58,944
What about makeup?

353
00:20:00,947 --> 00:20:03,515
I feel like it doesn't matter what I see.

354
00:20:03,583 --> 00:20:05,984
It matters what he sees.

355
00:20:09,391 --> 00:20:11,327
I feel like I gave him everything

356
00:20:11,395 --> 00:20:13,030
and I got nothing.

357
00:20:13,098 --> 00:20:15,232
Oh.

358
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:17,467
I could see she was gonna crack.

359
00:20:17,535 --> 00:20:19,469
Allison?

360
00:20:19,536 --> 00:20:21,170
Are you all right, dear?

361
00:20:25,975 --> 00:20:29,577
- It's okay. She'll be all right.
- Should I...

362
00:20:29,645 --> 00:20:31,412
If she wanted to be around us,
she would've stayed.

363
00:20:33,715 --> 00:20:38,051
Sarah, what do you do that makes
you feel good about the way you look?

364
00:20:38,119 --> 00:20:39,852
I feel kind of responsible.
Do you mind?

365
00:20:43,390 --> 00:20:46,091
Is there any kind of ritual?

366
00:20:46,159 --> 00:20:48,559
I think my strategy was right.

367
00:20:48,627 --> 00:20:50,261
They just want to get married

368
00:20:50,329 --> 00:20:51,929
and they'll buy anything that'll help.

369
00:20:56,234 --> 00:20:59,936
- Are you all right?
- Oh, it's you.

370
00:21:00,004 --> 00:21:01,505
Come with me.

371
