419
00:23:51,010 --> 00:23:53,311
if you would not say shitty things
about me behind my back.

420
00:23:54,513 --> 00:23:55,980
What?

421
00:23:56,048 --> 00:23:58,349
Come on. Are you gonna
deny it and make it worse?

422
00:23:58,416 --> 00:24:00,517
I don't know what you've heard,
but it's not true.

423
00:24:00,585 --> 00:24:03,219
You didn't call me an all-american idiot

424
00:24:03,287 --> 00:24:04,620
who fell into everything?

425
00:24:05,989 --> 00:24:07,889
Whom did I supposedly say this to?

426
00:24:07,957 --> 00:24:09,357
Does it matter?

427
00:24:09,425 --> 00:24:12,293
Well, I'd like to defend myself.

428
00:24:12,361 --> 00:24:14,995
I heard that you told your wife
that I was driving the tractor

429
00:24:15,063 --> 00:24:17,263
