that you were involved...

432
00:24:21,936 --> 00:24:25,171
We all were...
And that it was your account.

433
00:24:25,239 --> 00:24:28,173
And Crane told me yesterday
you said I was marrying for money.

434
00:24:28,241 --> 00:24:30,742
I didn't say that. He did.

435
00:24:30,810 --> 00:24:33,210
Well, he's like that and everybody
who knows him knows that.

436
00:24:33,278 --> 00:24:36,079
But when you say it... And especially
when it gets back to my fiancee...

437
00:24:36,147 --> 00:24:38,947
Trudy knows her, you know...
Some garden club.

438
