gets all the credit

468
00:26:08,470 --> 00:26:10,805
and you're spinning your wheels
half the time.

469
00:26:12,574 --> 00:26:14,508
Right now we're chasing Mountain dew.

470
00:26:14,576 --> 00:26:16,777
