00:27:38,392 --> 00:27:40,426
We made a mistake

492
00:27:41,695 --> 00:27:45,064
and I feel like it's awkward

493
00:27:45,132 --> 00:27:49,001
and it's better for both of us if I move on.

494
00:27:49,069 --> 00:27:51,904
I don't think that's necessary.
We're both adults.

495
00:27:51,972 --> 00:27:54,440
No, I really would feel better about it.

496
00:27:54,507 --> 00:27:58,476
A friend of mine told me
about a job at a magazine

497
00:27:58,544 --> 00:28:02,547
and I thought that might be interesting,
working for a woman.

498
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:05,750
Anyway, I...

499
00:28:07,753 --> 00:28:10,755
I would appreciate it if you could
write me a recommendation.

500
00:28:10,823 --> 00:28:13,491
Absolutely.
What would probably be even better

501
00:28:13,559 --> 00:28:16,060
is if you type up whatever you want
and I'll sign it.

502
00:28:17,696 --> 00:28:20,631
- What?
- You've been sparkling in your duties.

503
00:28:20,699 --> 00:28:22,934
Just put it on my stationery,
put whatever you want and I'll sign it.

504
00:28:37,183 --> 00:28:39,317
I don't say this easily,

505
00:28:39,385 --> 00:28:41,919
but you're not a good person.

506
00:28:45,291 --> 00:28:46,892
Allison, hold on.

507
00:29:03,911 --> 00:29:05,411
What's going on?

508
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,615
I'm gonna need a new secretary.

